<div class="alert-m">
  <div class="alert-c" style="margin-top: 30px">
    <% if @wx_mp_user.try(:qrcode_url) %>
      <div class="qrcode_image" style="text-align: center">
        <%= image_tag(@wx_mp_user.qrcode_url, width: '80%') %>
      </div>
      <br>

      <p><span class="alert-num">1</span>请<span class="alert-text">长按</span>并<span class="alert-text">识别图中的二维码</span></p>
      <p><span class="alert-num">2</span>点击<span class="alert-text">关注</span>公众号【<%= @wx_mp_user.try(:nickname) %>】</p>
      <p>如果已关注，请打开该公众帐号回复<span class="alert-text"><%= @keyword ||  @activity.try(:keyword) %></span>，参与此活动。</p>
    <% else %>
      <div class="alert-img"></div>
      <p>请先关注公众帐号</p>
      <p><span class="alert-num">1</span>点击右上角<span class="alert-text">分享按钮</span>查看公众号</p>
      <p><span class="alert-num">2</span>在【添加朋友】—【查找公众号】中搜索</p>
      <p><span class="alert-btn"><%= @wx_mp_user.try(:nickname) %></span>（长按可复制）</p>
      <p>如果已关注，请打开该公众帐号回复<span class="alert-text"><%= @keyword ||  @activity.try(:keyword) %></span>，参与此活动</p>
    <% end %>
  </div>
  <div class="alert-f">
    <a href="<%= mobile_root_path %>" class="alert-f-btn J-close">我知道了</a>
  </div>
</div>